<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink153">
<l>veḷḷāṅ kurukiṉ piḷḷai cetteṉak</l>
<l>kāṇiya ceṉṟa maṭanaṭai nārai</l>
<l>yuḷara voḻinta tūvi kulavumaṇaṟ</l>
<l>pōrviṟ peṟūun tuṟaivaṉ kēṇmai</l>
<l>naṉṉeṭuṅ kūnta ṉāṭumō maṟṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>Oh, will the [lady with] good, long tresses </l>
        <l>Seek intimacy with the man from the ghat</l>
       <l>In which the wader with an inexperienced gait that went to see</l>
      <l>Because the hatchling of the white wader had died, </l>
        <l>Obtained in heaps of gleaming sand feathers that it hid, having shaken [them] off?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
